name: Collision in 60 Seconds
description:
Made for No Code Jam #2

Theme: One Minute

Controls: D or Right Arrow Key to move, interact or continue text

You are heading towards an asteroid and your Autopilot is malfunctioning. You only have 60 seconds before disaster strikes.

Gamedesign & Music by hrschkfr

Made with Bitsy by Adam Le Doux

also used Borksy by Andrew Yolland , Bitsymuse by David Mowatt

Music made with Ableton 10
